---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sobre nosotros">
  <main class="bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-500">
    <section
      class="h-full ml-10 pt-36 w-1/2 text-white gap-5 grid place-content-center"
    >
      <h1 class="font-extrabold text-3xl">Los Pichy Boys & Su Equipo</h1>
      <blockquote class="italic font-extralight text-lg">
        Los Pichy Boys son el super-dúo humorístico conformado por los Cubanos
        Alejandro González y Maikel Rodríguez. Los Pichy Boys, que son primos
        por parte de madre, comenzaron haciendo pequeños videos por el año 2007
        para Youtube en su casa que poco a poco alcanzaban más visitas. Hoy día
        se han convertido en celebridades internacionales con su podcast, Somos
        Los Pichy Boys junto a su banda de secuaces. Únete a la banda usando el
        hashtag #TeamPichyBoys
      </blockquote>
      <p class="text-sm">Alejandro Y Maikel, son Los Pichy Boys</p>
    </section>

    <section
      class="h-full flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-36 py-20"
    >
      <article>
        <h1 class="font-extrabold text-6xl text-yellow-500">#TeamPichyBoys</h1>
      </article>
      <article class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-5">
        <picture class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
          <img
            src="/images/ale.webp"
            alt="ale"
            class="group-hover:scale-125 transition-all"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute capitalize text-yellow-200 flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-10 pt-5 pl-5 opacity-95 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-900 w-full h-full -bottom-full z-10 transition-all group-hover:-bottom-72"
          >
            <strong class="opacity-100 text-white text-3xl"
              >Alejandro [Pichy]</strong
            >
            <p>@LosPichyBoys</p>
          </div>
        </picture>

        <picture class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
          <img
            src="/images/maikito.webp"
            alt="maikito"
            class="group-hover:scale-125 transition-all"
          />

          <div
            class="absolute capitalize text-yellow-200 flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-10 pt-5 pl-5 opacity-95 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-900 w-full h-full -bottom-full z-10 transition-all group-hover:-bottom-72"
          >
            <strong class="opacity-100 text-white text-3xl"
              >Maikel [Maikito]</strong
            >
            <p>@LosPichyBoys</p>
          </div>
        </picture>
        <picture class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
          <img
            src="/images/gustavo.webp"
            alt="gustavo"
            class="group-hover:scale-125 transition-all"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute capitalize text-yellow-200 flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-10 pt-5 pl-5 opacity-95 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-900 w-full h-full -bottom-full z-10 transition-all group-hover:-bottom-72"
          >
            <strong class="opacity-100 text-white text-3xl text-nowrap">
              Gustavo [La Maquina]</strong
            >
            <p>Camarógrafo & Editor De Videos</p>
          </div>
        </picture>
        <picture class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
          <img
            src="/images/lopez.webp"
            alt="lopez"
            class="group-hover:scale-125 transition-all"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute capitalize text-yellow-200 flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-10 pt-5 pl-5 opacity-95 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-900 w-full h-full -bottom-full z-10 transition-all group-hover:-bottom-60"
          >
            <strong class="opacity-100 text-white text-3xl">
              Alex [Lopez] Lopez</strong
            >
            <div>
              <p>Productor Técnico</p>
              <p>¿Comediante?</p>
              <p>@AlexDWaves</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </picture>
        <picture class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-lg">
          <img
            src="/images/machete.webp"
            alt="machete"
            class="group-hover:scale-125 transition-all"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute capitalize text-yellow-200 flex flex-col items-start justify-start gap-10 pt-5 pl-5 opacity-95 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-900 w-full h-full -bottom-full z-10 transition-all group-hover:-bottom-60"
          >
            <strong class="opacity-100 text-white text-3xl">
              Mikey [Machete]</strong
            >
            <div>
              <p>Productor Creativo</p>
              <p>Digital Marketing Expert</p>
              <p>@MikeyMachete</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </picture>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

